Name: Olympus
Description:
Stukov's Capital Ship. Can dispatch dropship to send Elite Agents to target location and use aircrafts to attack enemy units.

Can attack the ground and air.

Root.Tooltip:
Sending out dropship to target location from Olympus, and dispatch six Guards of Apollo. Elite Marine. Guards of Apollo can use stim pack.

Can attack the ground and air.
Root.Name: Guard of Apollo

Root.Tooltip:
Sending out dropship to target location from Olympus, and dispatch three Spares of Ares. Elite Marauder. Spares of Ares can stun enemy units within an area.

Can attack ground.
Root.Name: Spare of Ares

Root.Tooltip:
Sending out dropship to target location from Olympus, and dispatch four Boots of Hermes. Elite Reaper. Boots of Hermes can use jetpack to switch between ground and flight modes at any time, and can throw KD8 bombs to cause a lot of AOE damage.

Can attack the ground and air.
Root.Name: Boots of Hermes

Root.Tooltip:
Sending out dropship to target location from Olympus, and dispatch four Shields of Athena. Elite Medic. Shields of Athena can heal ally unit and grant them additional positive effect.

Cannot attack.
Root.Name: Shield of Athena

Root.Tooltip:
Sending out dropship to target location from Olympus, and dispatch three Flames of Hephaestus. Elite Agent Hellion Tank. Hephaestus Burners can cause AOE damage to enemy units and can use jetpack assaults.

Can attack the ground.
Root.Name: Flame of Hephaestus

Root.Tooltip:
Sending out dropship to target location from Olympus, and dispatch two eyes of Hades. Elite Agent Ghost. The Eye of Hades is permanently invisible, and can guide the Orpos Satellite Cannon and release locked missiles.

Can attack the ground and air.
Root.Name: Eye of Hades

Root.Tooltip: Olympus is equipped with several Interceptors that can automatically attack enemy units near the base.
Root.Name: Olympus Carrier Aircraft

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Upgrades this Stargate to a Warp Stargate, allowing it to warp in air units to any location powered by a Pylon or Warp Prism.
Root.Name: Transform to Warp Stargate

Root.Tooltip: Warp Gate research affects Stargates and Robotics Facilities, allowing them to warp units in to any location with Pylon power.
Root.Name: Warp Harmonization

Root.Tooltip: Multi-functional anti-air Fighter. After applying Origa tribe protocol, it can use Anti-Matter Annihilate Bomb and Shield Battery. **Can attack the ground and air**
Root.Name: Warp In Scout

Root.Tooltip:
Flying Caster. Can use Stasis Ward.**Can attack ground units**
Detector
Root.Name: Warp In Oracle

Root.Tooltip: This ability unlocks at Commander Level 8.
Root.Name: Transform To Warp Stargate

Root.Tooltip:
Surgical strike craft. Attacks charge up for extra range and extra damage versus armored targets.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Warp in Void Ray

Root.Tooltip:
Area assault craft. Can use Destruction Beam to attack multiple units.

Can attack ground and air units.
Root.Name: Warp in Destroyer

Root.Tooltip: Main battleship. Able to build and launch interceptors to attack the enemy. After applying for the Origa tribe Protocol, you can use Research to use orbital bombing.**Can attack the ground and air**
Root.Name: Warp in Carrier

Root.Tooltip:
Purifier Faction
Siege artillery craft. Attacks from long range. Can use Disintegration.**Can attack ground and air units**
Root.Name: Warp In Tempest

Root.Tooltip:
Purifier Faction
Siege artillery craft. Attacks from long range. Can use Disintegration.**Can attack ground and air units**
Root.Name: Warp in Tempest

Root.Tooltip: This unit unlocks at Commander Level 11.
Root.Name: Warp in Tempest

Root.Tooltip: Olympus gathers special forces, and you can deploy them any time with a carrier ship. You can deploy them every 90 seconds.
Root.Name: Olympus Carrier Ship
